javafx.geometry

Enum Pos

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Pos>
      • javafx.geometry.Pos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Pos>

    public enum Pos
extends Enum<Pos>
    A set of values for describing vertical and horizontal positioning and alignment.
    Since:
    JavaFX 2.0
